This paper involves the use of machine learning methods for text analysis, specifically in the field of radiology reports. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The use of self-supervised learning and deep neural networks also suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a likely category. The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the use of radiology reports suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) may also be a relevant category.
